# ::snt Most people feel unintelligent and awkward when they first get to uni- you're definitely not alone there. But I would really recommend that you get an appointment with your uni counselling services.                         :degree (vv6 / most)))

                        :quant (vv10 / many))))

                        :ARG2 (vv16 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (vv18 / day)))
                  :mod (vv19 / still)
                  :quant (vv14 / many)))
      :snt2 (vv20 / and
            :mode interrogative

                        :domain (vv24 / that))
                  :op2 (vv25 / time
                        :mod (vv26 / even)
                        :mod (vv27 / still)))
            :op2 (vv28 / extent

                        :name (vv31 / name
                              :op1 "OCD"))
                  :mode interrogative)
            :op2 (vv32 / extent
                  :mod (vv33 / any))))

# ::lemmas ["the", "dynamics", "at", "the", "ORGANIZATION_1", "be", "that", "official", "from", "the", "country", "do", "not", "want", "to", "be", "obstacle", "to", "COUNTRY_1", "which", "be", "the", "largest", "country", "and", "the", "COUNTRY_2", "which", "be", "the", "most", "powerful", "country", "."]
# ::pos_tags ["DT", "NNS", "IN", "DT", "NNP", "VBP", "IN", "NNS", "IN", "DT", "NNS", "VBP", "RB", "VB", "TO", "VB", "NNS", "TO", "NNP", "WDT", "VBZ", "DT", "JJS", "NN", "CC", "DT", "NNP", "WDT", "VBZ", "DT", "RBS", "JJ", "NN", "."]
# ::ner_tags ["O", "O", "O", "O", "ORGANIZATION", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "COUNTRY", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "COUNTRY", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O", "O"]
# ::abstract_map {"ORGANIZATION_1": {"type": "named-entity", "span": "NSG", "ner": "ORGANIZATION", "ops": "NSG"}, "COUNTRY_1": {"type": "named-entity", "span": "India", "ner": "COUNTRY", "ops": "India"}, "COUNTRY_2": {"type": "named-entity", "span": "United States", "ner": "COUNTRY", "ops": "United States"}}
# ::tgt_ref dynamics want person have-org-role country COUNTRY_2 official obstacle and country COUNTRY_1 country include country powerful most COUNTRY_2 country COUNTRY_1 obstacle
# ::tgt_pred dynamic want - person have-org-role country official obstacle and country country large most name "India" country country powerful most name "United" "States" organization name "NSG"
# ::save-date Mon Aug 26, 2013 ::file PROXY_LTW_ENG_20070930_0021_17.txt
(vv1 / dynamics
      :domain (vv2 / want-01
            :ARG0 (vv3 / person
                  :ARG0-of (vv4 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (vv5 / country
                              :name (vv6 / name
                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States"))
                        :ARG2 (vv7 / official)))
            :ARG1 (vv8 / obstacle
                  :domain (vv9 / and
                        :op1 (vv10 / country
                              :name (vv11 / name
                                    :op1 "India"))
                        :op2 (vv12 / country
                              :ARG1-of (vv13 / include-91
                                    :ARG2 (vv14 / country
                                          :mod (vv15 / powerful
                                                :degree (vv16 / most))
                                          :name (vv17 / name
                                                :op1 "United"
                                                :op2 "States")))))
                  :topic (vv20 / obstacle))
            :polarity -))

      :ARG0 (vv2 / image
            :name (vv3 / Satellite)
            :source (vv4 / newspaper
                  :name (vv5 / name
                        :op1 "Institute"
                        :op2 "for"
                        :op3 "Science"

                                          :op1 "Arak")))
                        :mod (vv12 / reactor
                              :mod (vv13 / research-01
                                    :ARG1 (vv14 / water))
                              :mod (vv15 / heavy))))
            :degree (vv16 / significant)
            :time (vv17 / between
                  :op1 (vv18 / date-entity
                        :month 2
                        :year 2008)
                  :op2 (vv19 / date-entity
                        :month 10
                        :year 2008))))

      :op1 (vv2 / say-01
            :ARG0 (vv3 / person
                  :name (vv4 / name
                        :op1 "Ochoa"))

                  :ARG0 (vv6 / country
                        :name (vv7 / name
                              :op1 "Venezuela"))
                  :ARG1 (vv8 / arm
                        :mod (vv9 / country
                              :name (vv10 / name
                                    :op1 "Russia")))
                  :polarity -
                  :time (vv11 / ever)
                  :time (vv12 / before)))
      :op2 (vv13 / suggest-01
            :ARG0 vv3
            :ARG1 (vv15 / do-02
                  :ARG0 (vv16 / person
                        :name (vv17 / name
                              :op1 "Chavez"))
                  :ARG1 (vv18 / it)
                  :ARG2 (vv19 / become-01
                        :ARG1 vv16
                        :ARG2 (vv21 / depend-01
                              :ARG1 (vv22 / country
                                    :name (vv23 / name
                                          :op1 "US"))
                              :polarity -)))))
